- Backtesting results must include:
  • Win rate (%)
  • Average R multiple
  • Net profit/loss
  • Max drawdown
  • Longest win/loss streak
  • Equity curve data
- Log every valid trade setup in a CSV or JSON file under /logs/.
- Include timestamp, symbol, direction, entry, stop, take profit, R multiple, position size, and result.
- Backtester must be deterministic — same data input = same result.
